{"tid":803642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"杜特爾特登日本加賀艦　分析指菲日圖制衡中國南海活動","createTime":"2018-09-02T12:17:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T13:15:41.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"35f54f5acbe1fa5eb631fcce24e9c580b0575741","tid":803642,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T12:17:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1415827_1_L_20180902200017.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1415827_1_L_20180902200017.jpg&h=89406d05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本海上自衛隊護衛艦「加賀號」到訪菲律賓，總統杜特爾特登艦參觀。<br />\n<br />\n「加賀號」停靠在菲律賓北部呂宋島的蘇比克港。杜特爾特登艦時，日本防衛政務官大野敬太郎與一眾船員迎接。<br />\n<br />\n杜特爾特去年6月，亦曾在蘇比克港登上日本「出雲號」護衛艦。分析說，菲律賓與中國在南海有主權爭議，菲律賓想顯示與日本關係密切，日本亦希望加強與菲律賓的防衛合作，制衡中國在南海的活動。<br />\n<br />\n「加賀號」全長248米，最多可搭載14架直升機，具備海上基地功能。中國官媒在「加賀號」去年3月開始服役時，曾經評論「加賀號」不是護衛艦，而是「准航母」，需要警惕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.zimedia.com.tw/s/QLKeLW-0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.zimedia.com.tw%2Fs%2FQLKeLW-0&h=0360a69f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3bc0fdbf3a1dd26c978d1c2a2ccb1566b521ea58","tid":803642,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T12:20:27.000Z","msg":"中國包圍網"},{"pid":"f272c56f757d21e6c6c4ac940ccdd27f7fdd8058","tid":803642,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T12:21:02.000Z","msg":"又然"},{"pid":"6f51e48ae969187af69b5f387be3b2df7e70144d","tid":803642,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f272c56f757d21e6c6c4ac940ccdd27f7fdd8058","tid":803642,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T12:21:02.000Z","msg":"又然"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T12:23:15.000Z","msg":"支那國當日應承比菲律賓D錢, 等極都無<br />\n<br />\n杜特爾特依家反枱"},{"pid":"7d153e68cdf61f89172a5652b61815173821bfb2","tid":803642,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T12:43:02.000Z"